[0m[49m[39m  160, 164[0m:[39m[49m | **Encryption** | S3: SSE-KMS for all buckets; DynamoDB: encryption at rest; OpenSearch: encryption at rest and node-to-node encryption; all transit over TLS; SageMaker: volume encryption on training and inference instances |
