[0m[49m[39m  162, 166[0m:[39m[49m | **CloudTrail** | Enabled: log all S3, SageMaker, and DynamoDB API calls for HIPAA audit trail |
[0m[49m[39m  163, 167[0m:[39m[49m | **GPU Instances** | SageMaker training: ml.p3.2xlarge or ml.g5.2xlarge minimum. Batch inference: ml.g5.xlarge. Budget for multi-day training runs. |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 164     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Sample Data** | Public surgical video datasets: Cholec80 (80 cholecystectomy videos with phase annotations), m2cai16 (tool and phase annotations), CholecSeg8k (semantic segmentation). These are research datasets; never use real patient video without IRB approval and proper de-identification. |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      168[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **Sample Data** | Public surgical video datasets: Cholec80 (80 cholecystectomy videos with phase annotations), m2cai16 (tool and phase annotations), CholecSeg8k (semantic segmentation). These are research datasets. Real patient video requires IRB approval and proper de-identification. |
[0m[49m[39m  165, 169[0m:[39m[49m | **Cost Estimate** | Processing: ~$2.50-$8.00 per procedure (MediaConvert + SageMaker inference). Training: ~$500-$2,000 per model training run (multi-day GPU). Storage: ~$1-2/month per procedure (S3 Intelligent-Tiering). OpenSearch: ~$200-500/month for a small domain. |
